## Custom Paths (Optional)

If your repo location differs from defaults:
```
REPO_PATH = "/path/to/dubu/repo"
```

## Notes

- Run `/setup` to have Dubu configure this file automatically
- The setup command will detect your OS and create appropriate paths
- You can manually edit this file at any time
